claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table of demographic characteristics and prior vaccination history for four vaccine groups (Fluzone IIV4, Fluarix IIV4, ccIIV4, RIV4) including sample sizes, age distributions, sex, race/ethnicity, study sites, and prior influenza vaccination rates. This table presents participant demographics and vaccination history; it does not provide any data on antigenic matching or confirm identical match with WHO- or FDA-selected flu strains, and therefore does not support the claim.
